
Our Promise
Regardless of age, body type, visible or invisible disability, ethnicity, sex characteristics, gender identity and expression, level of experience, education, socioeconomic status, nationality, personal appearance, race, religion, or sexual orientation, we as members, contributors, and leaders promise to ensure that everyone participating in our community is free from harassment.


We commit to acting and interacting in a way that promotes a friendly, inclusive, diverse, open, and healthy community.
